10A3Ecommerce platform for watch listings.As a user I must be able to see a list of available watches for sale as well as filter and search them.IntermediateCusmuliuc Ciprian GabrielFor reference: https://www.chrono24.com/ and ebay.com , possibly even olx.ro as a smaller use-case.
42
As a user I must be able to list a watch for sale, upload photos, write a description and insert complex watch characteristics.Please read about: Angular, Spring Boot (Google it, there are many tutorials).
43
As a user I must be able to buy and pay the item.Must read: https://martinfowler.com/articles/microservices.html
44
As a user I must be able to do all actions in under 1s (loading time).Must read: https://martinfowler.com/articles/richardsonMaturityModel.html
45
As a user I must be able to communicate with the seller via a messaging mechanism.Since Web knowledge might be minimal, it would be good to know some HTML and CSS but also some basic JavaScript (JavaScript != Java ) (also Google).
46
As a user I must be able to login, register and reset password.Please refresh knowledge on OOP, Databases.
47
As a user I must be able to put watches to a favorites list.Please read a bit about OAuth2 and the authorization flow.
48
There are many requirements not present here.
